General.Name: Changzhou Zhongying Science & Technology Co. Ltd
General.Description: Changzhou Zhongying Science & Technology Co., Ltd engages in the research and development, production, and sale of high-frequency communication materials for printed circuit board manufacturers. Its products include PTFE, hydrocarbon, and special composite high-frequency microwave copper clad laminates for use in base station antennas, power amplifiers, low noise amplifiers, filters, coupler, aerospace, satellite communications, satellite television, military radar, electronic warfare systems, global positioning systems, microwave components, microwave modules, and other fields; and polymer composites. The company was founded in 2006 and is based in Changzhou, the People's Republic of China.
